data.description: Gorgeous end-unit townhome centrally located in Holly Springs. Lives like a detached home! This home has been meticulously cared for, and beautifully landscaped. Solar panels for low utility bills! Two car garage. Screened porch that backs to wooded area.Open floor plan with large dining area, and fireplace in living room. Large well laid out kitchen with stainless appliances, large island with seating. You won't believe the amount of storage you have here. Large owners suite with walk in closet and ensuite bath with oversized shower. Easy stroll to downtown Holly Springs shopping/dining/events in downtown Holly Springs. Five minutes to I-540 access.
